WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.680 --> 00:00:04.730
&gt;&gt; From the Library of
Congress in Washington, DC.

00:00:08.190 --> 00:00:09.830
&gt;&gt; Jane McAuliffe:
Well good morning.

00:00:09.830 --> 00:00:13.400
Good morning on this
very rainy day, alas.

00:00:13.400 --> 00:00:17.390
And welcome to the
History and Biography Stage

00:00:17.390 --> 00:00:20.150
of this year's National
Book Festival.

00:00:20.150 --> 00:00:22.760
We're delighted to see
all of you here and want

00:00:22.760 --> 00:00:30.420 position:56%
to extend a special welcome to those
who are watching us live on C-Span.

00:00:30.420 --> 00:00:35.640
