They don't get close.

00:12:18.160 --> 00:12:19.460
You can unpin it.

00:12:19.460 --> 00:12:21.250
Tom, can you help her so she can
just hold it a little closer?

00:12:21.250 --> 00:12:24.240
&gt;&gt; Thomas Oliphant:
I'm good for something.

00:12:24.240 --> 00:12:25.670
&gt;&gt; Kathy McKeon: Hold like this.

00:12:25.670 --> 00:12:27.370
&gt;&gt; Mary Louise Kelly: Hold it up.

