00:12:42.500 --> 00:12:43.800
&gt;&gt; Mary Louise Kelly: Aw.

00:12:43.800 --> 00:12:45.100
&gt;&gt; Kathy McKeon: So I was
very proud that she came

00:12:45.100 --> 00:12:46.400
to my wedding and the guests.

00:12:46.400 --> 00:12:47.700 position:56%
&gt;&gt; Mary Louise Kelly: Oh, of course.

00:12:47.700 --> 00:12:49.000
It's lovely.

00:12:49.000 --> 00:12:50.300
&gt;&gt; Kathy McKeon: Yes.

00:12:50.300 --> 00:12:51.600
And that's a picture of my wedding.

00:12:51.600 --> 00:12:52.900
&gt;&gt; Mary Louise Kelly: Alright.

00:12:52.900 --> 00:12:54.200
&gt;&gt; Kathy McKeon: This
picture was up in Cape Cod.

00:12:54.200 --> 00:12:55.880 position:56%
&gt;&gt; Mary Louise Kelly: Hold it just a
