00:12:58.110 --> 00:13:00.870
&gt;&gt; Kathy McKeon: This
picture was taken in Cape Cod.

00:13:00.870 --> 00:13:02.170
John --

00:13:02.170 --> 00:13:03.470
&gt;&gt; Mary Louise Kelly: Cape Cod.

00:13:03.470 --> 00:13:04.770
OK.

00:13:04.770 --> 00:13:06.070
&gt;&gt; Kathy McKeon: Yeah.

00:13:06.070 --> 00:13:07.370
John and Madame riding the horse.

00:13:07.370 --> 00:13:10.040
John wasn't a big fan of horses,
but that was Colin's little pony

00:13:10.040 --> 00:13:14.570
and then she outgrew the pony
