00:13:14.570 --> 00:13:15.870
But he got a --

00:13:15.870 --> 00:13:17.260
&gt;&gt; Mary Louise Kelly:
And here we are.

00:13:17.260 --> 00:13:19.070
He's younger there, it looks like.

00:13:19.070 --> 00:13:22.700
&gt;&gt; Kathy McKeon: This picture
