segregation in interstate travel

00:18:27.210 --> 00:18:31.880
and tried to trap those
freedom riders inside.

00:18:31.880 --> 00:18:36.600
They finally managed to
break out but this was one

00:18:36.600 --> 00:18:38.770
of the early horrible incidents

00:18:38.770 --> 00:18:41.430
that Kennedy really didn't
pay that much attention to.

00:18:41.430 --> 00:18:46.320
