00:19:45.590 --> 00:19:50.800
of the protesters and
lacerated their skin.

00:19:50.800 --> 00:19:57.670 position:56%
And the police, under the really
aggressive police chief Bull Connor,

00:19:57.670 --> 00:19:59.960 position:56%
